\f0\b0 \cf0 The impact of social media and what it has done to us and for us...it has connected us and that is a good thing (don't sound like an old crotchety person here)\
\
Attention Economy\
\
Social media in and of itself isn't bad...it connects families from long distances, helps us find relevant information about a place we like, and allows us to see and interact with people we would have otherwise never met...it's awesome!\
\
But there is a problem...a deeper below the surface alligator underneath the beautiful surface of pics and stories we all share with each other...comparison\
\
They have a vested interest in keeping you and your eyes glued to that screen...and it is working...\
Look up stats on how much time the average person spends on their phone...obviously that is not all on doom scrolling but a large amount of it is...and it's damaging us...\
\
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

